/usr/lib64/lustre/tests/test-framework.sh: line 5683: cannot create temp file for here-document: Read-only file system
pdsh@onyx-32vm11: gethostbyname(&quot;lctl&quot;) failed
/usr/lib64/lustre/tests/test-framework.sh: line 5683: cannot create temp file for here-document: Read-only file system
